At the far end of the bay admist the crates and various Predacon
tech, 
Hysteria sat. She was hunched over a small engine filter, when 
suddenly sparks followed by a short cry of surprise erupted from 
behind the nearest crate. Hysteria tumbled backwards, knocking over 
several crates in the process. She brushed the dust from her fur and 
stood:

"Well if ya ask me, and I know ya didn't, this is suicide." 

Hysteria tossed the broken filter aside:

"And we're short one engine filter. Any suggestions?"
